news.title: Gurugram administration approves demolition & sealing of illegal units in DLF phases 1 to 5
news.para: While 4,500 properties had been identified for violations earlier, 2,100 units now face demolition and sealing drive that is set to begin from April 4, following orders from Punjab and Haryana high court.

news.title: Contractor penalized for delays in TNUHDB projects in Chennai
news.para: The 118.53 crore project at Andimaniyam Thottam, ward 126, Mandavelli, aims to deliver 702 residential units using pre-fabricated concrete technology within 18 months.

news.title: Lucknow: LDA unveils discounts to sell over 1,000 unsold flats
news.para: Despite launching a ‘first come, first served' scheme during Diwali, which was initially extended until Mar 31 and has now been further prolonged, the LDA struggled to find takers for these properties.
